metadata.name: Lilac Coloured Funk
metadata.description:
AI + Digital painting, 2022

find me in locus  
kaleidoscopic eyes  
crushed like cherry  
blurry wanna focus  
helium delirium  
tight as a ballon  
stuck in space of droids and clones  
and it goes pop pop pop  
pop wow  
they mixing with my atoms  
say I make the grade

Usually I start with a digital painting made in Procreate or Photoshop, or just a text prompt. I then process it in Stable Diffusion and/or Dalle2. I paint on the output to change things I want different, tweak it or make major changes like add collage elements. Run it again with AI. This process goes on until I feel it is in balance and has a voice and a tone that speaks my language.
